8409%2Findia-solar-power-electricity-bill-savings%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20thermal%20energy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20not%20solar%20panels.%20That%20means%20instead%20of%20converting%20sunlight%20into%20electricity%2C%20it%20uses%20mirrors%20to%20concentrate%20sunlight%20and%20generate%20heat%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20kitchen%20is%20powered%20by%2084%20Scheffler%20reflectors%20%E2%80%94%20these%20are%20giant%20oval-shaped%20mirrors%2C%20each%20with%20a%20surface%20area%20of%209.2%20square%20metres.%20Their%20job%3F%20To%20track%20the%20sun%20and%20reflect%20its%20rays%20to%20a%20single%20focal%20point.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reflectors%20are%20mounted%20on%20rotating%20frames%20that%20follow%20the%20sun%20all%20day.%20This%20movement%20helps%20them%20capture%20maximum%20solar%20energy%2C%20just%20like%20sunflowers%20do!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20sunlight%20to%20steam%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20magic%20happens.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20sunlight%20hits%20the%20reflector%E2%80%99s%20focal%20point%2C%20temperatures%20can%20shoot%20up%20to%20800%C2%B0C%20%E2%80%94%20that%E2%80%99s%20hot%20enough%20to%20melt%20lead!%20This%20intense%20heat%20is%20used%20to%20create%20steam%2C%20which%20is%20what%20powers%20the%20kitchen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201920px)%20100vw%2C%201920px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Flq_5-2_11zon-1752819521.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221920%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22World%E2%80%99s%20Largest%20Solar%20Kitchen%20India%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Flq_5-2_11zon-1752819521.jpg%201920w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Flq_5-2_11zon-1752819521-300x125.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Flq_5-