dia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2Flq_india-one-solar-thermal-power-plant-brahma-kumaris_13993984261_o-1_11zon-1752819514-150x85.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471979%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EEach%20reflector%E2%80%99s%20concentrated%20light%20is%20directed%20onto%2042%20specially%20designed%20steel%20receivers%2C%20which%20absorb%20the%20heat%20and%20convert%20water%20into%20steam%20%E2%80%94%20over%203%2C500%20kilograms%20of%20steam%20every%20day(Image%20courtesy%3A%20brahmakumaris.org).%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20also%20systems%20in%20place%20to%20ensure%20smooth%20operations%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cul%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20water-softening%20unit%20to%20avoid%20mineral%20buildup%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EA%20pressure%20reducer%20to%20keep%20the%20steam%20flow%20consistent%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAnd%20a%20diesel%20backup%20system%20(only%20used%20during%20the%20monsoon)%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20during%20cloudy%20days%20and%20rain%2C%20the%20kitchen%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20stop.%20That%20backup%20diesel%20setup%20keeps%20meals%20flowing%2C%20making%20it%20reliable%20year-round.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%2020%2C000%20to%2050%2C000%20meals%20a%20day%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20this%20system%20was%20first%20fully%20commissioned%20in%201998%2C%20it%20was%20designed%20to%20cook%2020%2C000%20meals%20a%20day.%20But%20it%20quickly%20outperformed%20expectations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20expanding%20the%20infrastructure%2C%20improving%20efficiency%2C%20and%20adding%20more%20modules%2C%20the%20kitchen%20now%20serves%20up%20to%2050%2C000%20people%20daily%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mix%20of%20residents%2C%20volunteers%2C%20guests%2C%20and%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20the%20equivalent%20of%20feeding%20an%20entire%20stadium%20every%20single%20day%20with%20sunlight!%3