20someone%20like%20me%2C%20a%20self-proclaimed%20nerd%2C%20couldn't%20fix%20his%20own%20phone%2C%20there%20had%20to%20be%20a%20market%20for%20repair.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20started%20buying%20broken%20phones%20and%20parts%2C%20learning%20to%20fix%20them%2C%20and%20selling%20the%20services%20on%20eBay%20and%20Craigslist.%20Soon%2C%20my%20friend%20David%20and%20I%20were%20meeting%20customers%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpanera-founder-workers-not-motivated-making-money-shareholders-ceo-therapy-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPanera%3C%2Fa%3E%20during%20lunch%20breaks%20to%20do%20on-the-spot%20repairs.%20That%20eventually%20led%20to%20our%20first%20uBreakiFix%20store%20opening%20in%20August%202009.%20The%20store%20outpaced%20our%20entire%20website's%20sales%2C%20and%20that%20success%20told%20us%20something%3A%20People%20didn't%20want%20to%20wait%20to%20mail%20out%20their%20devices.%20They%20needed%20fast%2C%20local%20solutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20next%20three%20years%2C%20we%20grew%20to%2047%20corporate-owned%20locations.%20We%20franchised%20in%202012%20and%20eventually%20scaled%20to%20about%20550%20stores%20by%20the%20time%20I%20stepped%20away%20in%202021.%20We%20were%20the%20authorized%20repair%20partner%20for%20Google%20and%20Samsung%2C%20had%20contracts%20with%20top%20carriers%20and%20insurers%2C%20and%20built%20proprietary%20tech%20to%20ensure%20consistency%20and%20efficiency%20across%20our%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20stepping%20back%2C%20I%20took%20time%20to%20reset%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0spent%20more%20time%20with%20my%20family%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20thought%20about%20what%20was%20next.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2232991cc6-d1d5-450b-a61d-93df6faf732a%5C%22%3EThe%20bagel%20pivot%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20next%20step%20came%20unexpectedly.%20A%20guy%20in%20our%20office%20started%20bringing%20in%20bagels%20on%20Fridays%2C%20and%20we%20were%20all%20blown%20away%20by%20the%20quality.%20The%20bagels%20were%20from%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%2C%20a%20small%20operation%20in%20Florida%20started%20by%20Jeff%20and%20Danielle%20Perera%2C%20who%20had%20grown%20from%20baking%20at%20home%20to%20selling%20at%20farmers%20markets%20and%20eventually%20opening%20a%20couple%20of%20shops.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20intrigued%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0not%20just%20by%20the%20product%2C%20but%20by%20the%20potential.%20I%20met%20Jeff%20and%20Danielle%2C%20heard%20their%20story%2C%20and%20saw%20parallels%20between%20their%20journey%20and%20the%20early%20days%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fhow-to-use-amazon-trade-in-program%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EuBreakiFix%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20bagels%20were%20exceptional%2C%20the%20business%20model%20simple%2C%20and%20the%20menu%20tight%3A%20just%20bagels%2C%20spreads%2C%20and%20coffee.%20That%20simplicity%20makes%20scaling%20easier%20and%20keeps%20the%20focus%20on%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20I%20saw%20an%20opportunity%20to%20bring%20the%20operational%20and%20tech%20know-how%20I%20developed%20in%20the%20tech%20repair%20world%20into%20food.%20We%20started%20building%20from%20that%20foundation%2C%20working%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-scale-up-small-business-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eways%20to%20scale%20a%20small%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20bakery-first%20concept%20while%20keeping%20the%20heart%20of%20what%20made%20the%20original%20Jeff's%20Bagel%20Run%20special.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20we%20have%2015%20stores%2C%20with%20six%20more%20opening%20in%20the%20next%20six%20weeks.%20It's%20going%20to%20be%20a%20busy%20summer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20see%20this%20as%20a%20short-term%20play.%20I%20want%20to%20be%20a%20%26quot%3Bbagel%20guy%26quot%3B%20for%20the%20rest%20of%20my%20career.%20What%20I%20missed%20most%20after%20leaving%20uBreakiFix%20was%20being%20part%20of%20a%20great%20team%2C%20working%20together%20toward%20something%20big.%20I've%20reunited%20with%20many%20of%20the%20same%20people%20from%20that%20era%2C%20and%20we're%20being%20much%20more%20intentional%20about%20building%20something%20sustainable%20this%20time%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0something%20we%20can%20all%20be%20proud%20of%20for%20the%20long%20haul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20we've%20gone%20even%20deeper%20into%20the%20tech.%20We%20built%20our%20own%20point-of-sale%20system%2C%20kitchen%20display%20system%2C%20and%20real-time%20integrations%20with%20delivery%20platforms%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fuber-doordash-anticompetitive-inflating-costs-unfair-business-practices-lawsuit-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUber%20Eats%20and%20DoorDash%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20system%20predicts%20sales%20patterns%20throughout%20the%20day%20and%20gives%20bakers%20real-time%20recommendations%20on%20what%20to%20make%20and%20when%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0all%20to%20maximize%20freshness%20and%20minimize%20waste.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20joke%20all%20the%20time%20that%20we're%20the%20most%20sophisticated%2015-store%20bagel%20chain%20the%20world's%20ever%20seen.%20It%20seems%20silly%20from%20the%20outside%20looking%20in%2C%20but%20we've%20got%20a%20full-stack%20development%20team%20and%20a%20full%20real%20estate%20team.%20We%20were%20built%20like%20a%20brand%20that's%20much%20bigger%20than%20ours%2C%20the%20technology%20that%20we%20have%20is%20really%20neat%2C%20and%20we're%20really%20excited%20to%20continue%20to%20leverage%20it%20and%20use%20this%20as%20the%20foundation%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-scale-up-small-business-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Egrow%20the%20business%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224e3a8fb6-5213-43da-a46b-329b7716cfd4%5C%22%3EScaling%2C%20without%20losing%20the%20soul%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20in%20our%20stores%20is%20made%20from%20scratch%2C%20within%20the%20four%20walls.%20The%20dough%20is%