%3D%5C%22Graphic%20of%20a%20brain%20with%20%24100%20bill%20projected%20onto%20it%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6879728bf748d8c055f5d7cb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224186%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EOsakaWayne%20Studios%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20of%20the%20top%20quant%20researchers%20in%20Two%20Sigma's%20history%20is%20starting%20his%20own%20hedge%20fund.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHao%20Zhang%20pioneered%20machine%20learning%20trading%20research%20at%20Two%20Sigma%2C%20generating%20billions%20in%20profits.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EZhang%20intends%20to%20launch%20Hippocampus%20Capital%20Management%20in%20early%202026%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20most%20prolific%20Wall%20Street%20investors%20you've%20never%20heard%20of%20is%20preparing%20to%20launch%20a%20hedge%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20never%20been%20written%20about%20in%20a%20mainstream%20news%20article%2C%20but%20in%20certain%20quant%20finance%20circles%2C%20Hao%20Zhang%20is%20a%20revered%20figure.%20For%2017%20years%2C%20up%20until%202024%2C%20the%20quant%20researcher%20produced%20some%20of%20the%20most%20valuable%20trading%20signals%20at%20%2460%20billion%20hedge-fund%20giant%20Two%20Sigma.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20pioneer%20in%20applying%20machine%20learning%20to%20markets%20at%20Two%20Sigma%2C%20Zhang%20is%20now%20planning%20to%20hang%20out%20his%20own%20shingle.%20He's%20in%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20talking%20to%20potential%20investors%20and%20hedge%20fund%20service%20providers%2C%20according%20to%20five%20people%20who've%20been%20briefed%20on%20the%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20intends%20to%20call%20his%20firm%20Hippocampus%20Capital%20Management%2C%20the%20sources%20said%2C%20and%20is%20targeting%20a%20launch%20date%20in%20early%202026%2C%20one%20of%20the%20people%20said.%20It's%20not%20clear%20how%20much%20capital%20he's%20looking%20to%20raise.%20Zhang's%20contract%20with%20Two%20Sigma%20prohibited%20him%20from%20raising%20money%20from%20investors%20before%20July%201%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndustry%20sources%20expect%20the%20launch%20to%20generate%20significant%20interest%20from%20investors%2C%20given%20Zhang's%20reputation%20and%20track%20record.%20His%20alpha%20research%20has%20been%20responsible%20for%20billions%20in%20trading%20profits%20for%20Two%20Sigma%20over%20the%20course%20of%20his%20career%2C%20the%20people%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20requests%20for%20comment.%20Two%20Sigma%20declined%20to%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ee92fbe2-774b-4724-82f6-dddcf1b6c4ab%5C%22%3EThe%20techniques%20'godfather'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETwo%20Sigma%2C%20which%20has%201%2C700%20employees%20today%2C%20was%20a%20comparatively%20small%20firm%20when%20it%20hired%20Zhang%20in%202007%2C%20operating%20in%20what%20was%20then%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethe%20secretive%20hedge%20fund%20niche%20of%20quant%20trading.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fund%20was%20on%20the%20vanguard%20of%20machine%20learning%2C%20an%20early%20artificial%20intelligence%20method%20that%20helps%20computers%20make%20decisions%20and%20predictions%2C%20and%20recognize%20patterns.%20Zhang%2C%20with%20his%20specializations%20in%20both%20stats%20and%20computer%20science%2C%20early%20on%20developed%20lucrative%20trading%20models%20focused%20on%20machine-learning%20non-linear%20techniques%20%E2%80%94%20uncovering%20complex%2C%20non-obvious%20patterns%20in%20market%20data%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epeople%20familiar%20with%20Zhang%20said.%20The%20group%20that%20evolved%20around%20such%20strategies%20took%20on%20different%20names%20over%20the%20years%2C%20but%20staff%20shorthand%20was%20often%20simply%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwo-sigma-exec-kan-huang-techniques-unit-joins-cubist-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Btechniques%3C%2Fa%3E.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Two%20Sigma%20would%20pursue%20other%20machine-learning%20initiatives%2C%20techniques%20became%20the%20crown%20jewel%20and%20a%20closely%20guarded%20secret.%20%3Cspan%3ESome%20refer%20to%20Zhang%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bgodfather%26quot%3B%20of%20the%20unit%2C%20according%20to%20former%20employees.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPeople%20familiar%20with%20Zhang%2C%20including%20two%20former%20Two%20Sigma%20employees%2C%20said%20the%20billions%20of%20dollars%20attributed%20to%20his%20trading%20models%20make%20him%20one%20of%20the%20top%20researchers%20in%20the%20company's%20nearly%2025-year%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20small%20footprint%20Zhang%20does%20have%20online%20comes%20from%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Euniversity%20press%20stories%20connected%20to%20his%20donations%20%E2%80%94%20which%20have%20ramped%20up%20in%20recent%20years%20%E2%80%94%20to%20the%20California%20Institute%20of%20Technology%20and%20the%20University%20of%20California%20at%20Berkeley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZhang%20transferred%20from%20Fudan%20University%20in%20Shanghai%20to%20Caltech%20in%201997%20to%20study%20engineering%20and%20applied%20science%2C%20later%20earning%20a%20master's%20in%20statistics%20and%20a%20Ph.D%20in%20computer%20science%20at%20UC%20Berkeley.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20training%20and%20education%20has%20been%20a%20cornerstone%20in%20my%20life%2C%26quot%3B%20Zhang%20said%20in%20the%202024%20announcement%20of%20his%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finspire.berkeley.edu%2Fo%2Fgenerosity-to-engineering-reflects-alums-view-of-berkeley-as-key-to-his-success%2F%3Futm_source%3Dchatgpt.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eendowment%20of%20a%20Berkeley%20professorship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20studying%20at%20Berkeley%2C%20Zhang%20lived%20with%20another%20math%20and%20stats%20whiz%20named%20Peng%20Zhao%2C%20according%20to%20several%20people%20who%20know%20them.%20Zhang%20joined%20Two%20Sigma%20after%20completing%20his%20doctorate%3B%20Zhao%20helped%20build