20likes%20to%20use%20is%20a%20listing%20optimization%20software%20called%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frankbreeze.com%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERankbreeze%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20It%20helps%20hosts%20fine-tune%20the%20description%20of%20their%20property%20and%20discover%20amenities%20that%20guests%20in%20their%20area%20are%20looking%20for.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20his%20favorite%20features%20is%20the%20A%2FB%20testing%2C%20which%20lets%20you%20change%20your%20cover%20photo%20or%20pet%20policy%2C%20for%20example%2C%20to%20see%20how%20it%20affects%20your%20Airbnb%20ranking.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221086%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22kent%20he%20family%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64836eb4323ab800198555f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22724%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAirbnb%20host%20Kent%20He%20and%20his%20family.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Kent%20He%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BOn%20Google%2C%20no%20one%20really%20goes%20to%20page%20five%20or%2010%20after%20searching.%20It's%20the%20same%20for%20Airbnb.%20You%20want%20to%20be%20ranked%20as%20high%20as%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20explained.%20%26quot%3BI%20use%20Rankbreeze%20to%20play%20around%20with%20my%20cover%20photos%20to%20see%20which%20one%20allows%20me%20to%20rank%20highest.%20I%20also%20play%20around%20with%20the%20listing%20title.%20For%20example%2C%20during%20colder%20months%2C%20I%20might%20highlight%20that%20we%20have%20a%20heated%20pool.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EYou%20could%20offer%20the%20best%20Airbnb%20property%20in%20your%20area%2C%20but%20if%20it's%20not%20properly%20marketed%2C%20guests%20may%20never%20see%20it.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEspecially%20with%20the%20cover%20photo%2C%20%26quot%3Bdon't%20waste%20that%20space%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20He.%20%26quot%3BBe%20intentional%20with%20your%20listing