sity.%20In%201992%2C%20he%20began%20farming%20with%20just%20half%20an%20acre%20of%20chillies.%20The%20yield%20earned%20him%20Rs%2045%2C000%2C%20which%20was%20not%20a%20windfall%2C%20but%20enough%20to%20spark%20hope.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Davinder%20Singh%20Mushkabad's%20farm%20from%20a%20bird's%20eye%20view.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-16T182750.947-1752670679-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471124%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDavinder%20Singh%20Mushkabad%E2%80%99s%20farm%20from%20a%20bird%E2%80%99s%20eye%20view.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20wife%2C%20Baljit%20Kaur%2C%20took%20up%20dairy%20farming%20to%20supplement%20the%20family%20income.%20Together%2C%20they%20saved%20and%20slowly%20expanded%20operations%20to%20ten%20acres%2C%20adding%20tomatoes%20and%20other%20seasonal%20crops%20into%20the%20mix.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20Davinder%E2%80%99s%20goals%20weren%E2%80%99t%20limited%20to%20daily%20sustenance.%20He