-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752666310-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752666310-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-16T171459.165_11zon-1752666310-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-471038%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESwuyievezo%20Dzudo%20has%20built%20a%20low-cost%20solar%20dryer%2C%20an%20electricity-free%20device%20that%E2%80%99s%20helping%20farmers%20preserve%20their%20produce%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20Porba%2C%20he%20began%20spending%20time%20with%20farmers%2C%20listening%20to%20their%20daily%20struggles.%20And%20somewhere%20in%20those%20conversations%2C%20he%20asked%20what%20they%20did%20with%20the%20leftover%20harvest.%20%E2%80%9CMost%20told%20me%20they%20had%20no%20reliable%20electricity%2C%20making%20it%20almost%20impossible%20to%20preserve%20their%20surplus%20crops%20properly.%20This%20led%20to%20huge%20losses%2C%20as%20the%20excess%20would%20simply%20rot%20or%20be%20turned%20into%20compost.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20infrastructure%20lagging%20far%20behind%2C%20many%20hilly%20parts%20of%20Nagaland%20still%20face%20severe%20power%20shortages%20%E2%80%94%20and%20when%20electricity%20is%20available%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20often%20too%20erratic%20to%20rely%20on.%20As%20Swuyievezo%20listened%20to%20the%20farmers%2C%20this%20recurring%20challenge%20kept%20surfacing.%20Over%20time%2C%20it%20became%20clear%20to%20him%20that%20any%20real%20solution%20would%20need%20to%20work%20without%20relying%20on%20power%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%E2%80%99s%20when%20he%20began%20exploring%20the%20idea%20of%20building%20a%20solar%20dryer%20%E2%80%94%20something%20simple%2C%20affordab