C%20or%20home%20product%20reflects%20the%20hands%20and%20stories%20behind%20it%2C%20infused%20with%20techniques%20like%20Kantha%2C%20Batik%2C%20natural%20dyeing%2C%20and%20tribal%20weaving.%20The%20label%20ensures%20that%20every%20design%20is%20co-created%20with%20the%20artisans%2C%20honouring%20their%20voice%20and%20creativity%2C%E2%80%9D%20Sonali%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDeshaj%20operates%20through%20direct%20sales%2C%20exhibitions%2C%20and%20curated%20partnerships%2C%20allowing%20full%20transparency%20and%20better%20earnings%20for%20the%20artisans.%20While%20the%20revenue%20varies%20depending%20on%20regular%20sales%2C%20exhibitions%20and%20events%2C%20nearly%2060%E2%80%9370%20percent%20of%20the%20earnings%20from%20each%20product%20go%20directly%20to%20the%20artisan%2C%20ensuring%20fair%20compensation%20and%20continued%20production.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20significant%20milestone%2C%20the%20empowered%20tribal%20women%20now%20run%20their%20own%20Common%20Facility%20Centre%20(CFC)%20%E2%80%93%20an%20initiative%20originally%20started%20by%20Sonali%20and%20Gopal%2C%20adjacent%20to%20Moram%20Earth.%20Here%2C%20over%20100%20women%20regularly%20engage%20in%20production%20and%20sales%20independently.%20The%20CFC%20includes%20dedicated%20units%20for%20dyeing%2C%20tailoring%2C%20handloom%20weaving%2C%20and%20packaging%2C%20as%20well%20as%20training%20spaces%2C%20hostels%2C%20and%20a%20canteen.%20This%20model%20has%20become%20a%20shining%20example%20of%20self-sustained%20rural%20entrepreneurship%20led%20by%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-07-15T195757.778_11zon-1752589994.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20homestay%20is%20designed%20to%20give%20guests%20the%20true%20feeling%20of%20slow%20living.%5C%22%20srcset%3