without%20room%20to%20breathe.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20perched%20in%20these%20mountains%2C%20he%20is%20planning%20another%20farm.%20It%20will%20not%20be%20a%20replica%20of%20his%20previous%20endeavour%3B%20it%20will%20be%20a%20fresh%20start%2C%20grounded%20in%20everything%20he%20learnt%2C%20yet%20seeking%20something%20richer%20%E2%80%94%20namely%2C%20community%20and%20belonging.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20grounded%20beginnings%20of%20a%20dream%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20journey%20began%20not%20in%20these%20cool%20heights%20but%20in%20the%20scorching%20heat%20of%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20on%20a%20five%E2%80%91acre%20stretch%20of%20red%20clay%20that%20he%20painstakingly%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F468218%2Fquit-mumbai-for-zero-waste-farm-mahabaleshwar-sustainable-farm-life-permaculture-handmade-products%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eturned%20into%20a%20permaculture%20sanctuary%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20land%20was%20never%20just%20soil%20and%20seed%2C%20it%20was%20a%20dream%2C%20a%20refuge%2C%20and%20ultimately%2C%20a%20teacher%20who%20showed%20him%20the%20cost%20of%20chasing%20peace%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135052.199_11zon-1752567676.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20Reddy%20left%20his%20high-paying%20job%20at%20a%20startup%20because%20he%20was%20working%20for%2015-16%20hours%2C%20and%20that%20led%20to%20a%20complete%20burnout%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135052.199_11zon-1752567676.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135052.199_11zon-1752567676-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135052.199_11zon-1752567676-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135052.199_11zon-1752567676-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135052.199_11zon-1752567676-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-470113%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20Reddy%20left%20his%20high-paying%20job%20at%20a%20startup%20because%20he%20was%20working%20for%2015-16%20hours%2C%20and%20that%20led%20to%20a%20complete%20burnout%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20pine%E2%80%91scented%20mornings%20of%20Manali%2C%20before%20the%20first%20furrow%20split%20the%20earth%2C%20there%20was%20the%20urgency%20of%20the%20city.%20%E2%80%9CI%20started%20working%20when%20I%20was%20still%20in%20school%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%2025-year-old%20recalls.%20%E2%80%9CBy%20Class%2012%2C%20I%20was%20making%20Rs%2030%2C000%20a%20month%20freelancing%20in%20graphic%20design%20and%20copywriting.%20College%20was%20not%20a%20part%20of%20the%20plan%20as%20I%20was%20already%20building%20a%20career%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20laughs%20at%20the%20memory%20of%20those%20teenage%20years%2C%20single%E2%80%91handedly%20picking%20up%20skills%20like%20design%2C%20animation%2C%20and%20marketing%2C%20until%20he%20resembled%20%E2%80%9Ca%20one%E2%80%91man%20agency%2C%E2%80%9D%20juggling%20multiple%20roles.%20That%20hustle%20propelled%20him%20to%20a%20creative%20director%20post%20by%20the%20age%20of%2021%2C%20with%20a%20salary%20few%20could%20fathom.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20crazy%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CEveryone%20thought%20I%20had%20it%20all.%E2%80%9D%20But%20as%20he%20recounts%20the%20unrelenting%2015%20to%2016%E2%80%91hour%20days%2C%20the%20nights%20without%20sleep%2C%20the%20constant%20rush%20to%20meet%20deadlines%2C%20you%20begin%20to%20sense%20the%20cost%20of%20that%20very%20success.%20%E2%80%9CI%20remember%20working%20through%20New%20Year%E2%80%99s%20Eve%20alone%20in%20the%20office.%20My%20boss%20told%20me%20to%20take%20a%20break%2C%20and%20I%20said%2C%20%E2%80%98I%E2%80%99ll%20rest%20when%20it%20is%20all%20done.%E2%80%99%20But%20that%20finish%20line%20kept%20moving.%20It%20was%20always%20just%20out%20of%20reach%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20crash%20that%20changed%20everything%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20of%20course%2C%20came%20the%20crash.%20%E2%80%9CIn%202023%2C%20I%20hit%20a%20wall%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20voice%20steady%20but%20reflective.%20%E2%80%9C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367326%2Ftoxic-workplaces-solutions-healthy-workplace-work-life-balance-work-pressure-employee-wellbeing%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurnout%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F367326%2Ftoxic-workplaces-solutions-healthy-workplace-work-life-balance-work-pressure-employee-wellbeing%2F%5C%22%3Eis%20not%20just%20being%20tired%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20is%20like%20breaking%20from%20the%20inside.%20I%20quit%20abruptly%2C%20with%20no%20plan%2C%20and%20just%20left%20everything%20behind%20because%20I%20could%20not%20take%20it%20anymore.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20half%20a%20year%2C%20he%20wandered%20through%20a%20haze%20of%20uncertainty.%20%E2%80%9CI%20did%20not%20know%20who%20I%20was%20outside%20of%20work.%20For%20so%20long%2C%20money%20and%20status%20had%20defined%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20That%20was%20when%20his%20mother%20reminded%20him%20of%20the%20farmland%20he%20had%20bought%20years%20earlier%20near%20Pamidi%20in%20Anantapur%2C%20a%20tract%20of%20red%20earth%20with%20a%20dry%20well.%20%E2%80%9C%E2%80%98You%20always%20wanted%20to%20retire%20on%20a%20farm%2C%E2%80%99%20she%20said.%20%E2%80%98Why%20not%20start%20now%3F%E2%80%99%20That%20question%20stayed%20with%20me.%20It%20felt%20like%20a%20call%20to%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20the%2025-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20started%20to%20experiment%20with%20permaculture%20once%20he%20moved%20to%20his%20farm%20near%20Pamidi%20in%20Anantapur%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T135604.153_11zon-1752567974-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-470121%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20started%20to%20experiment%20with%20permaculture%20once%20he%20moved%20to%20his%20farm%20near%20Pamidi%20in%20Anantapur%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArriving%20at%20the%20farm%20was%20both%20relief%20and%20reckoning.%20He%20remembers%20the%20parched%20soil%2C%20the%20dry%20well%2C%20and%20the%20overgrown%20stream%20bed.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20not%20a%20lush%20paradise.%20But%20I%20did%20not%20want%20a%20traditional%20farm%20either%2C%20so%20this%20worked%20out%20for%20me.%20I%20wanted%20a%20food%20forest%2C%20a%20place%20where%20every%20plant%20supports%20another%2C%20water%20is%20conserved%2C%20and%20the%20land%20heals%20itself%2C%E2%80%9D%20Abhishek%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20immersed%20himself%20in%20permaculture%20principles%2C%20learning%20to%20layer%20the%20landscape%20with%20tall%20canopy%20trees%2C%20like%20mangoes%2C%20guava%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20mid%E2%80%91level%20nitrogen%20fixers%20such%20as%20moringa%2C%20which%20he%20calls%20a%20%E2%80%9Cmiracle%20tree%2C%E2%80%9D%20because%20it%20grows%20fast%2C%20enriches%20soil%2C%20and%20feeds%20soil%20and%20people%20alike.%20It%20also%20had%20low%E2%80%91lying%20ground%20covers%20like%20sweet%20potato%2C%20sweet%20peas%2C%20butterfly%20pea%2C%20and%20brahmi%20to%20hold%20moisture%20and%20guard%20against%20erosion.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWater%20remained%20the%20fiercest%20challenge%20for%20the%20young%20boy%2C%20trying%20to%20build%20a%20life%20on%20a%20farm%20in%20the%20Obulapuram%20village%20near%20Pamidi.%20The%20well%20had%20dried%20up%2C%20and%20the%20stream%20flowed%20only%20in%20the%20monsoon.%20So%20he%20and%20his%20mother%2C%20Neela%20Reddy%2C%20dug%20swales%2C%20trenches%20carved%20along%20the%20contours%20of%20the%20land%20to%20catch%20and%20hold%20rainwater.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20gruelling%20work%2C%20in%20the%20midday%20sun%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls%2C%20pausing.%20%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20the%20first%20monsoon%2C%20the%20soil%20drank%20deeply%20and%20the%20land%20greened.%E2%80%9D%20They%20installed%20drip%20irrigation%20for%20efficiency%2C%20and%20later%20added%20sprinklers%20for%20areas%20with%20dense%20ground%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20introduced%20chickens%20to%20scratch%20the%20soil%20and%20fertilise%20it%2C%20later%20brought%20in%20bees%20to%20aid%20with%20pollination%2C%20and%20added%20compost%20worms%20to%20speed%20up%20the%20breakdown%20of%20organic%20waste%20into%20nutrient-rich%20soil.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140010.351_11zon-1752568225.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhishek%20grew%20all%20kinds%20of%20crops%20in%20his%20farm%20in%20a%20systematic%20way%20so%20that%20the%20plants%20could%20support%20each%20other%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140010.351_11zon-1752568225.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140010.351_11zon-1752568225-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140010.351_11zon-1752568225-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140010.351_11zon-1752568225-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140010.351_11zon-1752568225-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-470126%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhishek%20grew%20all%20kinds%20of%20crops%20in%20his%20farm%20in%20a%20systematic%20way%20so%20that%20the%20plants%20could%20support%20each%20other%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESeeds%20of%20doubt%2C%20roots%20of%20hope%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20extended%20family%2C%20who%20had%20lived%20there%20for%20generations%2C%20and%20neighbouring%20farmers%20who%20had%20worked%20the%20land%20for%20years%2C%20regarded%20him%20with%20mild%20suspicion.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20thought%20I%20had%20lost%20my%20mind%3B%20just%20some%20city%20boy%20thinking%20he%20could%20farm%20the%20desert%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20every%20new%20sprout%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F399647%2Farup-kumar-ghosh-kolaghat-marigold-farming-tennis-ball-variety-successful-farm-entrepreneur%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eevery%20budding%20flower%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20every%20stabilised%20trench%2C%20slowly%20turned%20suspicion%20into%20wonder.%20That%20first%20harvest%2C%20including%20tomatoes%2C%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20ladyfinger%2C%20bitter%20gourd%2C%20and%20leafy%20greens%2C%20was%20modest%2C%20yet%20hard-won.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20was%20an%20overwhelming%20satisfaction%20in%20eating%20something%20I%20had%20grown%20with%20my%20own%20hands%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20once-barren%20plot%20grew%20more%20than%2035%20different%20crops%2C%20which%20is%20living%20proof%20of%20the%20power%20of%20learning%20and%20experimenting.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20order%20to%20share%20both%20the%20triumphs%20and%20tribulations%20of%20this%20farming%20life%2C%20he%20created%20an%20Instagram%20account%20called%20%E2%80%98Silly%20Sensei%E2%80%99.%20%E2%80%9CI%20wanted%20to%20show%20the%20real%20stuff%2C%20something%20that%20textbooks%20and%20traditional%20farmers%20were%20not%20teaching%20to%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20interested%20in%20knowing%20about%20this%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20His%20candid%20posts%20struck%20a%20chord%20and%20drew%20more%20than%20700%2C000%20followers.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20like%20that%2C%20I%20am%20so%20enthusiastic%20to%20teach%20them%20about%20farming%20and%20how%20we%20can%20live%20a%20healthy%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140423.420_11zon-1752568475.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22He%20also%20introduced%20chickens%20to%20the%20farm%20to%20scratch%20the%20soil%20and%20fertilise%20it%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140423.420_11zon-1752568475.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140423.420_11zon-1752568475-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140423.420_11zon-1752568475-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140423.420_11zon-1752568475-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F07%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-07-15T140423.420_11zon-1752568475-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-470132%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%